cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and connection rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting pusch_AntennaPorts to 0 will cause invalid antenna port configuration and physical layer initialization failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 pusch_AntennaPorts 設定為 0 會導致無效的天線埠配置，並造成物理層初始化失敗。
